<ab facs="#facs_359_r1l14">vnd gemachet <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> da ſein ſol cʒü <expan>Perching<ex>en</ex></expan> auf den <expan>nehſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
