<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Stephan, als
                            <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Hilpolt
                            <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Prunne
                            <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwas habe
                            <expan>aufgehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, also ist
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ein teyding getroffen und ein
                                <expan>frewntlich<ex>er</ex></expan> tag beredt und gemachet,
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> da sein sol czü
                                <expan>Perching<ex>en</ex></expan>, auf den
                        <app><note><q type="date"><expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mont<ex>ag</ex></expan></q>In Frage kommen 05./12./19./26.10./02.11.1411</note></app> cze nacht da cze sein und <app><note><q type="date">auf den eritag</q>In Frage kommen 06./13./20./27.10./03.11.1411</note></app> frü
                        da <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>cze r<ex>e</ex>d<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir auf <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und da bey den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein wollet; und getrawen
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>sünderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol, daz ir uns des nicht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>saget</expan>. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Schenke<ex>n</ex></expan> czü <expan>Gey<ex>e</ex>rn</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
